{
  "stem": "11998.5",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And he kept saying, hand on, hang on, the war is almost over.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Hitler's not going to win it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And there's no way that he's going to win the war.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And by '43, you know-- that was after the-- the-- the-- I think, the attack on Leningrad that they started in 1942, I guess.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "So they were already being driven back.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "So the war looked not so good for the-- for the Nazis anymore.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And I manufactured these things.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And I would sell it to him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "I would give it to him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "I would go about past my father's place, and I would drop it on the-- on the bench, and keep on walking, or pretending that I delivered some material.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And he would take it, and he would sell it to his-- or-- the kapi between-- he'd sell it to the other people that lived in the barracks, because they confiscated all hot plates.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And this thing, you could put in a glass of water, and it would boil.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "But it wasn't-- basically, two wires with two metals, pieces of metal, separated by a piece of [INAUDIBLE] light, and became a-- it was boiling by electrolysis.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And they-- they really liked it, because they confiscated all the hot plates.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "So if they want to have a cup of tea in the evening, they couldn't have it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So this was a very hot item.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I manufactured this as soon-- as fast as I could, without giving-- making obvious that parts were disappearing.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he would either give my-- my father a piece of bread, or he would drop a bag into the garbage bin as I was walking by, so that I could retrieve it.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because there's no fraternization between the people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that's how we worked.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
